灣初創都去左廣東省搵投資"},{"pid":"9e00e19fda3a3a7d3689bb4f056e00fcb693697b","tid":684434,"uid":17510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T21:38:40.000Z","msg":"馬英狗遺禍"},{"pid":"1d5be9b4aad659d163a30d6699c000e569d7ca61","tid":684434,"uid":51129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T21:52:03.000Z","msg":"上面係咁強調2017做乜？2017好舊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbead17a4ed075d2261f89248cd9a4f9041e3544","tid":684434,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:01:32.000Z","msg":"大家要搞清楚，人地只係去海外工作，而唔係移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要對付共匪，就只係拎佢啲錢，唔需要認同佢地嘅政治理念，正如對付建制派，只係擺佢地着數，投票嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d9b7f4aa4b2210b893f92cc5eaad56b9dcb22a","tid":684434,"uid":12241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:28:43.000Z","msg":"咁事實上計返發展前景人工<br />\n大陸一線城市北京上海深圳一定比台灣好<br />\n其實台灣最top果班都會出去揾食<br />\n留低既都係果堆冇能力毒撚<br />\n後生仔係台灣真係冇前途 養生咩"},{"pid":"be9ac651286e69e846d38e274f33f129f6f030f2","tid":684434,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:36:41.000Z","msg":"識個fd台灣妹真係 打算去，可能易溝通"},{"pid":"89ae793d615f04bac9949aaa0b828fbf82b781f3","tid":684434,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:45:39.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"a51daa18003df02ea2f49165da45361f767f0a72","tid":684434,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:25:53.000Z","msg":"但係支那狗又隻隻想嚟香港發展？"}]}